      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 294
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Kanade",
      "Body": "—So, I have a little something to discuss... I ended up making three demos yesterday, so I want you to listen to them later.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 0,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 294,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-shy",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 296
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Ena",
      "Body": "Three!? Isn't that amazing!? I mean, we haven't even made the next video yet...!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 296,
          "MotionName": "w-cute01-forward03",
          "FacialName": "face_surprise_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 296,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_08_80_19",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 294
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Kanade",
      "Body": "As I was thinking, a lot of different things just came out...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 0,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 294,
          "MotionName": "w-kanade16-lookdown",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ahaha. That's so like Kanade.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute01-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_08_82_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 295
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mafuyu",
      "Body": "Should we go to SEKAI and listen to them after this?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 295,
          "MotionName": "w-normal08-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_normal_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 295,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_08_83_18",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 294
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Kanade",
      "Body": "Yeah, I'd appreciate that. Also—",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 0,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 294,
          "MotionName": "w-kanade16-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(...Niigo is an important place to me.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal01-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_07",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_08_85_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(Even if... even if I end up working hard towards my dream, I don't want to let it go. It's a precious place.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-trouble",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_08",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_08_86_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(So, the only thing I can do is—)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-relief",
          "FacialName": "face_serious_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_08_87_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(Just work hard until I can't keep up with everyone anymore.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_angry_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
